data.description: Charming 1910 home in Caldwell, ID. This 3-bed, 2-bath residence features 1065 sqft of cozy comfort. With a well-appointed kitchen and abundant natural light. Outside, new landscaping and a vinyl fence create an inviting outdoor retreat. With a 2-car garage, this home offers convenience and functionality. Situated in a desirable location, this home provides easy access to freeway, local amenities, schools, and parks. Don't miss the chance to own a piece of Caldwell's history. Schedule a showing today!
